item.title: CVE-2023-0592|2024-08-02T05:17:50.162Z -- sviehb -- jefferson
item.description: A path traversal vulnerability affects jefferson's JFFS2 filesystem extractor. By crafting malicious JFFS2 files, attackers could force jefferson to write outside of the extraction directory.This issue affects jefferson: before 0.4.1.
